		<title>每次一抱貓咪就掙扎？其實是牠正在抗議「這件事」</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/10/%e6%af%8f%e6%ac%a1%e4%b8%80%e6%8a%b1%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%b0%b1%e6%8e%99%e6%89%8e%ef%bc%9f%e5%85%b6%e5%af%a6%e6%98%af%e7%89%a0%e6%ad%a3%e5%9c%a8%e6%8a%97%e8%ad%b0%e3%80%8c%e9%80%99%e4%bb%b6%e4%ba%8b/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 10 Nov 2025 02:00:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
