		<title>貓咪真的有「超能力」？揭開牠與生俱來的5種驚人天賦</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/09/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e7%9c%9f%e7%9a%84%e6%9c%89%e3%80%8c%e8%b6%85%e8%83%bd%e5%8a%9b%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e6%8f%ad%e9%96%8b%e7%89%a0%e8%88%87%e7%94%9f%e4%bf%b1%e4%be%86%e7%9a%845%e7%a8%ae%e9%a9%9a%e4%ba%ba/</link>
		
